{"title":"给Aurora主题增加图片CDN","uid":"6c7e8ce860d8756553dd1d8f84913e5a","slug":"AddPictureCDN","date":"2021-08-14T13:53:32.000Z","updated":"2022-06-01T12:55:15.753Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/AddPictureCDN.json","keywords":"编程,笔记,生活,感悟,诗歌,音乐,影视,博客,Hexo","cover":"/images/RaumzeitBlog/202108142153647.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"情景引入\"><a href=\"#情景引入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"情景引入\"></a>情景引入</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>由于<code>github</code>不支持百度爬虫的爬取，且在国内访问速度较慢，所以我选择将<code>hexo</code>部署到自己的服务器上。<br>为了减轻服务器的压力，我选择为图片资源加上<code>CDN</code>，但是国内<code>CDN</code>需要域名备案，所以我选择将图片放在<code>github</code>上，再采用<code>jsdelivr</code>加速。<br><a href=\"https://www.jsdelivr.com/\">jsDelivr</a> <code>YYDS</code></p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"在Deploy中加入github仓库\"><a href=\"#在Deploy中加入github仓库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"在Deploy中加入github仓库\"></a>在Deploy中加入github仓库</h2><div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">提示</p>\n<p>由于要上传到<code>github</code>，所以可以使用<code>hexo</code>的<code>deploy</code>插件，在上传网站文件的时候，就直接上传图片，然后将本站链接替换为<code>jsdelivr</code>链接，即可，这样就少去了使用<code>picgo</code>上传图片的步骤。</p>\n</div>\n<p><code>deploy</code>填写格式：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-yaml\" data-language=\"yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">deploy:\n- type: git  \n  repo:  \n   github: git@github.com:MeerOst&#x2F;meerost.github.io.git,master # 这里填写你的github仓库链接(ssh形式)，和分支</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"修改markdwon的生成模板\"><a href=\"#修改markdwon的生成模板\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改markdwon的生成模板\"></a>修改<code>markdwon</code>的生成模板</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>由于<code>markdown</code>图片格式为 <code>![图片描述](图片链接)</code>，而且，我们在写作时，为了方便，都是直接使用拖动图片至编辑器的习惯，所以需要修改<code>markdwon</code>的生成模板中关于图片链接的代码。</p></blockquote>\n<p>打开文件 <code>node_modules\\hexo-renderer-marked\\lib\\rederer.js</code>，找到131大概行。如图，将代码:<br><a data-fancybox=\"gallery\" href=\"/images/2021/08/14/15681ed0-12fb-42d5-9ed9-ebc2a04bc633.png\"><img src=\"/images/2021/08/14/15681ed0-12fb-42d5-9ed9-ebc2a04bc633.png\" alt=\"jsdelivr图片CDN\"></a></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">let out &#x3D; &#96;&lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;$&#123;encodeURL(href)&#125;&quot;&#96;;\n    if (text) out +&#x3D; &#96; alt&#x3D;&quot;$&#123;text&#125;&quot;&#96;;\n    if (title) out +&#x3D; &#96; title&#x3D;&quot;$&#123;title&#125;&quot;&#96;;\n    if (lazyload) out +&#x3D; &#39; loading&#x3D;&quot;lazy&quot;&#39;;\n\n    out +&#x3D; &#39;&gt;&#39;;</code></pre>\n\n<p>改为：<br><a data-fancybox=\"gallery\" href=\"/images/2021/08/14/2a4c6e28-5f1f-43ec-9adb-1afc04ff529e.png\"><img src=\"/images/2021/08/14/2a4c6e28-5f1f-43ec-9adb-1afc04ff529e.png\" alt=\"jsdelivr图片CDN\"></a></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;&#x2F;判断链接是否为本地链接\n    var translateUrl&#x3D;&#96;$&#123;encodeURL(href)&#125;&#96;;\n    if(translateUrl.indexOf(&quot;http&quot;)&#x3D;&#x3D;-1)\n    &#123;\n      &#x2F;&#x2F;请将https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;MeerOst&#x2F;meerost.github.io@master改为你的github仓库在jsdelivr中的链接\n      translateUrl&#x3D;&#96;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;MeerOst&#x2F;meerost.github.io@master$&#123;encodeURL(href)&#125;&#96;;\n    &#125;\n    let out &#x3D; &#96;&lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;$&#123;translateUrl&#125;&quot;&#96;;\n    if (text) out +&#x3D; &#96; alt&#x3D;&quot;$&#123;text&#125;&quot;&#96;;\n    if (title) out +&#x3D; &#96; title&#x3D;&quot;$&#123;title&#125;&quot;&#96;;\n    if (lazyload) out +&#x3D; &#39; loading&#x3D;&quot;lazy&quot;&#39;;\n\n    out +&#x3D; &#39;&gt;&#39;;</code></pre>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">注意</p>\n<p>请将代码中的链接<code>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/MeerOst/meerost.github.io@master</code>改为你的github仓库在<code>jsdelivr</code>中的链接，如，这里的<code>MeerOst</code>为作者账户名称（非昵称），<code>meerost.github.io</code>为仓库名称，<code>master</code>为分支名称。</p>\n</div>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>由于代码会自行判断链接为本站链接还是外站链接，所以只要你的<code>markdown</code>在填写本地链接时，正确填写，生成站点文件时就会自动替换为<code>jsdelivr</code>链接。</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"markdown中的图片引用\"><a href=\"#markdown中的图片引用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"markdown中的图片引用\"></a><code>markdown</code>中的图片引用</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>由于<code>markdown</code>的填写格式类似这样：<code>![图片描述](/images/name.png)</code>，这样，主题在生成时，才会在<code>public</code>文件夹下，创建<code>images</code>文件夹，并将图片文件存于文件夹下。<br>所以为了填写方便，你可以结合<code>Hexo</code>桌面客户端（<a href=\"https://github.com/gaoyoubo/hexo-client\">HexoClient</a>）使用<br>下载安装<code>HexoClient</code>（建议选择1.3.5版本，1.3.6已经不支持这个功能了）后，在写文章时将图片拖至要写文字的地方，<code>HexoClient</code>就会自动生成<code>markdown</code>的图片引用。</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"结果展示\"><a href=\"#结果展示\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"结果展示\"></a>结果展示</h2><h3 id=\"HexoClient\"><a href=\"#HexoClient\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"HexoClient\"></a>HexoClient</h3><p><a data-fancybox=\"gallery\" href=\"/images/2021/08/14/76637249-196c-47f9-98aa-8c3faf30a753.png\"><img src=\"/images/2021/08/14/76637249-196c-47f9-98aa-8c3faf30a753.png\" alt=\"HexoClient\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"站点\"><a href=\"#站点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"站点\"></a>站点</h3><p><a data-fancybox=\"gallery\" href=\"/images/2021/08/14/a38e41d3-2fed-4daa-be5f-a9772b9971d1.png\"><img src=\"/images/2021/08/14/a38e41d3-2fed-4daa-be5f-a9772b9971d1.png\" alt=\"jsdelivr图片CDN\"></a></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 1